lead_paragraph: As far as U.S. Open encores go they don't come much tougher than the act Roberta Vinci has to follow after pulling off one of the biggest upsets ever at a grand slam during her magical run to last year's final.

headline.print_headline: Vinci Gives Herself Tough U.S. Open Act to Follow
